{"tid":862034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"死左膠屌你老母","createTime":"2018-10-14T14:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T03:10:07.000Z","uid":77959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa06c5f37e16ebec40593d99f48ab07bbe1820f","tid":862034,"uid":77959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:33:56.000Z","msg":"今日去咗左膠個遊行，本身都知佢哋無乜作為嫁啦，估唔到真係on99咁<br />\n<br />\n遊完行係政總集會，搵班人上去講人工島有乜問題，我屌你老母難得今日團結咗咁多人，你走嚟做論壇，都唔撚識運用manpower<br />\n<br />\n之後有班巴絲打號召衝大台，見住佢哋一衝上台就比成比左膠打，仲要口口聲聲話巴絲打人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話佢哋係咪想比全香港市民知佢哋唔係和平集會，我屌死攬爛攬和平個字做乜柒啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好笑嘅係，左膠口講和平，但就郁手去打巴絲，有個男人好似想打死人咁發狂去打人，呢啲叫和平？而家仲開始係fb抹黑係巴絲打人在先，仲有個區議員入院做證據<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦成班虛偽左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ba8041e2b4cbb1098f7c4fc81360d3f7757dae","tid":862034,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"今日先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297573bccd00989ddd6fc7b0c0b25cd542ec0532","tid":862034,"uid":77959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無諗過佢哋真係咁撚無恥<br />\n在場班人仲想扯開巴絲打啲口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  攞明想佢哋死<br />\n而家仲要扮無發生過，調轉頭話番佢哋係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db19bbd2ba6eeb0c64f93cff692ac5d34ba69fb","tid":862034,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"泛民：<br />\n畀啲掌聲自己！！<br />\n大家記得投票！！<br />\n記得捐錢科水畀我地！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets